dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.service.spec.rfs.role.VPNSecurityServiceSpecRole
dataStructure.description:
This class defines the specific type of security that is required to implement a particular CustomerFacingVPNService in terms of ResourceFacingServiceSpecRoles. Thus, it represents all of the invariant characteristics necessary to build a VPNSecurityService, abstracted in terms of ServiceSpecificationRoles. Please see the DEN-ng MPLS VPN model for more details.

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: VPNSecurityServiceSpecRole
